flowchart LR
    APR["ArchitecturePromptRecord<br/>captures architecture-relevant intent"]
    AP["ArchitectureProposal<br/>structures a proposed change"]
    DC["DecisionCandidate<br/>not accepted doctrine"]
    PG["ProofGate<br/>required evidence before promotion"]
    AHF["ArchitectureHealthFinding<br/>blocked action / drift / overclaim risk"]
    Lifecycle["Decision lifecycle workflow<br/>accepted / deferred / rejected / superseded<br/>not started"]
    Evidence["Tracked evidence<br/>source anchors / tests / runtime proof when needed"]
    Review["Independent review gate<br/>R038 remains active"]

    APR --> AP --> DC
    DC -->|requires proof| PG
    PG -->|may surface| AHF
    PG -->|must be satisfied by| Evidence
    DC -->|future workflow controls| Lifecycle
    Review -->|future proof-heavy gate| Lifecycle

    DC -. "candidate only" .-> Lifecycle
    PG -. "gate row is not gate satisfaction" .-> Evidence
    AHF -. "diagnostic, not product proof" .-> Evidence
    Lifecycle -. "future workflow, not authority yet" .-> Evidence
